name: Medabots
description:
Medabots styled model Trained with the Anything 4.5 checkpoint with 169 images at 100 epochs per image. Works well with a CFG of 3 - 7.5 and a clip skip of 1-4. Key Trigger Word is MedabotsV1

Version 2 was trained on the RevAnimated Model with 369 images at 50 epochs per image. works well with 3-7.5 cfg and a clip skip of 1-4. Trigger word is MedabotV2

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description: New Version Trained with RevAnimated with 369 images at 50 Epochs. CFG of 3 - 7.5 Keyword MedabotV2
